The goal is to prove that `@appendLists α (@appendLists α as bs) cs = @appendLists α as (@appendLists α bs cs)` for arbitrary lists `as`, `bs`, and `cs` of elements of type `α`. This is essentially the associativity of the `appendLists` function (which is just `++` notation for lists).

